1912
01:24:34,180 --> 01:24:37,597
(grand orchestral music)

1913
01:24:38,476 --> 01:24:41,327
- All aboard, track 23, all aboard!

1914
01:24:41,327 --> 01:24:42,767
- What you're doing is so great.

1915
01:24:42,767 --> 01:24:45,579
