1919
01:24:57,032 --> 01:25:00,159
- I've come this far, I might
as well shoot for the moon.

1920
01:25:00,159 --> 01:25:01,522
- Oh, good for you!

1921
01:25:01,522 --> 01:25:02,456
- That's terrific.

1922
